Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.70,0:00:05.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.53,0:00:09.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小涼宮春日的憂鬱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.68,0:04:13.68,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}翻譯：NT000A；後期：zipwinmax。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.95,0:00:12.49,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬聖節派對\N10/31\N不給糖就搗蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.75,0:00:14.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  來過萬聖節吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.01,0:00:16.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說得像去京都旅行一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.03,0:00:20.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此  快提供些和萬聖節相關的訊息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.89,0:00:21.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…說來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.34,0:00:24.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該需要南瓜和蝙蝠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.21,0:00:28.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為阿虛太沒用  只能麻煩古泉了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.44,0:00:29.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.94,0:00:33.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從展開上看  裝作不知道比較有趣  所以我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.71,0:00:35.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛…古泉也不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.86,0:00:36.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在聽什麼啊  春日！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.12,0:00:38.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算啦  隨便玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.03,0:00:39.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認真聽啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.95,0:00:41.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先來準備
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.55,0:00:43.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算從哪裡開始？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.38,0:00:45.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  這是唯一的情報源
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.12,0:00:49.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然到處都能吐槽  但先不管這些了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.24,0:00:51.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盯——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.98,0:00:57.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罩著南瓜的披風男纏繞著蝙蝠怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.76,0:01:00.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我也這麼想…但應該不太對
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.87,0:01:03.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南瓜買來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.68,0:01:04.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買的人是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.10,0:01:05.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.03,0:01:06.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.67,0:01:08.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Get！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.59,0:01:10.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.11,0:01:15.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦  刻臉太麻煩了…就想把阿虛的臉壓上南瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.46,0:01:18.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相當硬的！ 別小看生南瓜！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.26,0:01:20.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就麻煩實玖瑠刻臉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.44,0:01:21.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.21,0:01:22.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有希幫下忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.80,0:01:23.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.75,0:01:26.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這期間去尋找些需要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.43,0:01:31.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長門同學  完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.96,0:01:34.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右眼眶大了3毫米
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.56,0:01:35.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.01,0:01:39.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次是左眼眶大了1毫米
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.48,0:01:40.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦～？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.20,0:01:43.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右嘴角短了1.5毫米
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.36,0:01:46.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右眼眶大了0.3毫米
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.71,0:01:49.54,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（半小時後—）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.99,0:01:50.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抽泣…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.04,0:01:53.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.57,0:01:55.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要的東西大部分都湊齊了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.97,0:01:58.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題是蝙蝠該怎麼辦…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.35,0:01:59.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲～小春
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.59,0:02:01.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝙蝠的話我家後院的洞穴中就有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.11,0:02:03.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.27,0:02:04.34,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就快去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.49,0:02:05.06,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.56,0:02:05.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來  為什麼會有人體模型…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.73,0:02:10.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是要把南瓜和披風等戴在這上面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.49,0:02:11.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.67,0:02:15.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺成了相當奇怪的東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.59,0:02:17.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是在供奉邪教的神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.22,0:02:20.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  原來是在準備萬聖節啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.06,0:02:23.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道就帶些糖果來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.35,0:02:24.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糖果？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.46,0:02:25.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到萬聖節就一定是那個了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.25,0:02:29.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送糖果給裝扮成怪物的小孩  好讓他們回去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.07,0:02:32.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  萬聖節原來是這樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.47,0:02:37.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從中途起  就一直認為\N這是供奉並信仰原創的神的活動而進行準備呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.75,0:02:38.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.00,0:02:41.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機會難得  就來供獻些糖果吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.61,0:02:42.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實玖瑠有糖果嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.12,0:02:43.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.97,0:02:45.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.89,0:02:46.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.95,0:02:49.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口袋裡有這個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.95,0:02:52.46,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（醃海帶）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.57,0:02:52.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我很疑惑這是不是可以歸在糖果一類裡面…不過算了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.27,0:02:53.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.13,0:02:55.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不給糖就搗蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.28,0:02:56.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尋覓與破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.15,0:02:59.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想要啊  扔給電腦研究會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.86,0:03:02.29,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（之後在鶴屋學姐家裡召開了盛大的派對）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.52,0:03:04.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.51,0:03:05.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.77,0:03:07.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然你才剛回來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.68,0:03:09.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一起出去買晚餐材料吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.79,0:03:11.29,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（一個人不敢外出）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.63,0:03:16.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對  這樣放在袋子裡就會很輕鬆…輕鬆…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.16,0:03:17.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別放我進去！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.70,0:03:17.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.82,0:03:20.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…但如果遇到貓的話…不…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.69,0:03:25.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.64,0:03:26.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.72,0:03:27.10,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（妥協點(手持)）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.26,0:03:30.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長門同學今天想吃什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.54,0:03:33.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餡有腰花的仔兔腿肉印度燒餅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.63,0:03:35.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪莉風味  添加人參濃湯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.89,0:03:39.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬鈴薯和蘿蔔很便宜呢  做咖喱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.24,0:03:41.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向右5步
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.34,0:03:42.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上升50釐米
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.00,0:03:43.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待機！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.23,0:03:45.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投入！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.65,0:03:49.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  來吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.17,0:03:52.17,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（晚上10點）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.32,0:03:59.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成這個身體後就不能熬夜了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.42,0:04:04.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長門同學明天還要上學  差不多該睡覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.97,0:04:08.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快睡！

